Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
I dont think it is a good idea that universities require freshman live on campus. Firstly, usually the rent in campus is higher than outside the college. You can not force people to pay more. Second, it should let students to choose where do they prefer to stay. 